---
<section class="py-24 bg-[#0A0A0A]">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mb-14">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[#F0F0F0] mb-6">What We Do</h2>
      <p class="text-[#9CA3AF] text-lg leading-relaxed">
        We build and install AI agents directly into your business. These are software programs that run on your systems, connect to your existing tools, and handle specific tasks automatically, without you touching them.
      </p>
      <p class="text-[#9CA3AF] text-lg leading-relaxed mt-4">
        This is not a chatbot on your website. This is not another SaaS platform you'll forget to cancel. This is custom automation, installed for your operation, running in the background while your team focuses on actual work.
      </p>
      <p class="text-[#9CA3AF] text-lg leading-relaxed mt-4">
        We don't rip out your existing software. Your inventory system, your dispatch tools, your invoicing platform. They stay. We build agents that fill the gaps, enhance reporting, and connect the pieces your current tools can't handle on their own.
      </p>
    </div>

    <h3 class="text-[#C9A84C] text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase mb-8">What agents actually handle</h3>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      {features.map((f) => (
        <div class="bg-[#111111] border border-white/5 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:border-[#C9A84C]/30 transition-colors duration-300">
          <div class="text-[#C9A84C] mb-4" set:html={f.icon} />
          <h3 class="text-[#F0F0F0] font-semibold text-lg mb-3">{f.title}</h3>
          <p class="text-[#9CA3AF] leading-relaxed">{f.body}</p>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
